## Error Handling
- Implement error boundaries for critical components
- Use try/catch blocks for error-prone operations
- Log errors with appropriate context information
- Create user-friendly error messages for display

## Validation
- Use zod for schema validation in forms and data
- Implement client-side validation before submission
- Show inline validation errors with clear messaging
- Validate user input as early as possible

## Error Recovery
- Implement auto-retry for network operations
- Create graceful fallbacks for failed operations
- Preserve user input during form submission errors
- Provide clear recovery instructions for users
